<HEADLINE>
KAZAN ACCEPTS AWARD TO CHEERS, INDIFFERENCE
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By PHIL DAVIS  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ &UR;  &LR; After a round of applause that included both
