</P>
<P>
   But heck, let's be charitable. It's the end of the millennium,
and everybody's a little out of whack about it. There's no reason
why this year's Oscars shouldn't fit right in with the overall
zeitgeist. Indeed, for both good and ill, the 71st Academy Awards
