<HEADLINE>
THE PERPETUAL-MOTION ECONOMY: THE STRONGER IT GETS, THE SWEATIER
THE PALMS 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.)  (The Week in Review)  
 (ART ADV: Graphic is being sent to NYT graphic clients.
Non-subscribers can make individual purchase by calling (888)
603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.)  
 (bl)  
 By LOUIS UCHITELLE   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
