</P>
<P>
   &UR; WHERE TO TEE IT UP &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; BUSINESS GOLF STRATEGIES &LR;  &QL; : $2,500 and up. Basking Ridge, N.J.
908-204-9350  &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; BUSINESSLINKS INTERNATIONAL &LR;  &QL; : $2,500 to $10,000 for a half to
full day.
Tampa, Fla. 813-269-7599  &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; DAN WEILBAKER'S STUDENT OUTING &LR;  &QL; : $100. West Chicago, Ill.
815-753-6216
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
