<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-TEST-HNS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THIS IS A TEST - THISIS A TEST  
 PLEASE DISREGARD -TEST -TEST  
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON--This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
   This is a test from the Hearst bureau
</P>
<P>
