<P>
   &UR; The Great Memory Debate &LR;
</P>
<P>
   Three guys are debating who has the best memory.
</P>
<P>
   First guy says, `I can remember the first day of my First Grade
class.`
</P>
<P>
   Second guy says, `I can remember my first day at Nursery
School!`
</P>
<P>
   Not to be outdone, the third guy says, `Hell, that's nothing. I
can
</P>
<P>
   remember going to the senior prom with my father, and coming
home with
</P>
<P>
   my mother.`
</P>
