<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-22 16:12 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9793 &Cx1f; ttf-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NYLITE(SMILE)-2TAKES-     03-22 1258
